cuPythia
========

cuPythia is an independent, from-scratch GPU (CUDA) reimplementation of parts of the
PYTHIA 8 event generator — the hard process, the final-state parton shower, Lund string
fragmentation, hadron decays, and supporting machinery — written to run device-resident,
one-event-per-thread, with a counter-based RNG for exact reproducibility.

